        <abstract> 
<p>JVC’s publisher [Schweizerbart] must decide soon how many copies of two maps in <hi rend="italic">Volcanic islands and South America</hi> are needed.</p>  
<p>Has sent new edition of <hi rend="italic">Orchids</hi> – greatly altered, but he hopes improved.</p> 
